mily:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">G4</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">的直推不少于</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">人，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">G5</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">的直推不少于</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">人，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">GS</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">经理的直推不少于</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">人，高级经理的直推不少于</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">人，否则无法完成升级。</span><span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n<b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">直推奖励：</span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">1、10%</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">（重复循环重复获得，交易成功后立即到账）</span><span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"background:white;\">\r\n		<b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">推荐奖励：</span></b><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\"> 1、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">代</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\"