t YaHei\';color:#999999;\"> 3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">、经理奖钱包每次提现范围为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">1000-5000</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">的倍数。每周</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">天</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">提现封顶</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">15000</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">。</span><span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\"> 4</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">、匹配后打款时间</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">小时，收款后确认时间</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">24</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">小时，违规则封号。</span><span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\"> 5</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">、超时未打款扣除上级金额</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">500.</span><span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\"> 6</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">、提现后匹配时间为</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">48</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\">小时。</span><span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#999999;\"> 7</span></span>